{"inkVersion":20,"root":[["^Good evening, Mr. Jenkins. ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^My name is Oliver White. ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^I'm here to ask you a few questions. ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Ah, the detective. ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^Just get on with it then. ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^What do you need to know? ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n",{"->":"Knot1"},["done",{"#f":5,"#n":"g-0"}],null],"done",{"Knot1":[["ev","str","^About last night","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},"ev","str","^About the family","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":4},"ev","str","^About the strange matter","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-2","flg":4},{"c-0":["\n","^Can you recount your activities from yesterday afternoon onward, Mr. Jenkins? ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^I was here, at the bar. ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^Started mid-afternoon, I reckon. ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^And you stayed here throughout the entire evening? ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^That's right. ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^I had no reason to leave. ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^Good company, good drinks, what more could a man want? ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: happy"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^Can anyone vouch for your whereabouts? ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Ask anyone here. ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^Bartender, servers, the ladies. They'll tell you the same. ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^I didn't step a foot out of this bar. ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n",{"->":"Knot1"},{"#f":5}],"c-1":["\n","^Can you describe your family dynamics to me, Mr. Jenkins?  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Well, detective, I've been treated rather well by my parents.  ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^We've had our disagreements, as any family does, but nothing more than that.  ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^I understand. And what about your brother?  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Does he share the same sentiments?  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Jonathan? No, he's always been the black sheep, unfortunately.  ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: sad"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^Dad never really understood him and his fascination with chemicals and such.  ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^Mum tries to mediate, but Dad's a stubborn one.  ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^Do you think your brother could have a motive to harm your father?  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^That's a strong accusation, detective.  ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: angry"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^Thomas isn't exactly in the best of terms with our parents, yes, but to go to the extent of murder?  ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: angry"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^I don't think so.  ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^It's just a possibility we need to consider, Mr. Jenkins.  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^What is your relationship with your brother?  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Despite our differences, and the way our parents feel about him, Thomas and I are rather close.  ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^He's family, after all.  ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^I would never believe he could do something this horrific.  ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: sad"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^Detective, there is something that has been bothering me, and I feel like it might be important.  ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n",{"->":"Knot1"},{"#f":5}],"c-2":["\n","^Is there something else that has been bothering you, Mr. Jenkins?  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^It's a bit embarrassing, Detective, but I can't seem to shake off this suspicion.  ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: sad"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^I've seen my mother and Mr. Abernathy, the assistant, together quite a lot recently.  ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: sad"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^It's probably nothing, but it has been bothering me.  ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: sad"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^Have there been any unusual incidents or conversations that caught your attention?  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Actually, yes.  ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: thinking"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^I found this letter at the bottom of my mother's drawer when I was looking through her things...  ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: sad"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^I shouldn't have, but I did.  ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: sad"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^Can I see the letter?  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Sure, here it is.  ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^It's signed by P.A., Philip Abernathy, and it talks about making preparations for something important.  ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^This is indeed suspicious.  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: thinking"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^The contents of this letter could suggest a number of possibilities.  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: thinking"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Do you think it could be... an affair?  ",{"#":"speaker: Arthur_Jenkins"},{"#":"portrait: sad"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^It's too soon to jump to conclusions, Mr. Jenkins.  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^It could mean many things.  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^However, I will take this into account during the investigation.  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Thank you for bringing this to my attention.  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: happy"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n",{"->":"Knot1"},{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"#f":1}],"listDefs":{}}